{
  "stem": "9963.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mengele came to the hospital where he emptied the hospital twice a week-- Monday and Friday, he came in and took all the people to the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't let people lay in that room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was six weeks over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But luckily, every time he came my card was pulled out and he said that I am a helper here, that I helping them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he took me and he saved my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Six weeks I was in the hospital because that didn't heal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see, if that didn't heal, you know, I was there for six weeks and it saved my life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After that, I came to the-- after the six weeks, I came to the work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I worked over there in a different barrack, in barrack nine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- I slept bad night, but I worked at the [NON-ENGLISH], this is where-- we were shoveling coals to the oven were making steam for the factories to work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was hard work sometimes, and not so hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When the wagons come we had to unload the-- the train, you know, this was on a time limit where it was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But later we could relax and was all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I met over there the kapo, and the-- and the foreman, and I did a lot of good things in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's so many things that I want to jump over this, and a little bit further.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because even over there, in Buna Auschwitz, I was able to do things what it is just unheard of.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I did it, and for that, what I made friends everywhere I was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In every place I was, I made myself friends to the point where they were ready to give their life for me.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
